{"tid":1848828,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】香港警察拍片為「武漢同胞」打氣近乎全蒙面 全片無提本地醫護","createTime":"2020-01-28T16:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T17:33:34.000Z","uid":127929,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4610f03dd1ca4c17b574c45620f89067e8fb3ace","tid":1848828,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:26:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TLDR 睇下面紅字</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200128/HEVVD6GUUXZL3O3H4J66MLLGT4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200128%2FHEVVD6GUUXZL3O3H4J66MLLGT4%2F&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGXdC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=1144cf9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200128%2FHEVVD6GUUXZL3O3H4J66MLLGT4%2F&h=c64e79c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200128/HEVVD6GUUXZL3O3H4J66MLLGT4/</a><br />\n因武漢低估及隱瞞，令武漢肺炎疫情在全球擴散，更令香港亦出現多宗由武漢旅客傳入的確診個案，本港前線醫護飽受壓力，更要照顧由內地赴港求診的確診或懷疑個案隔離患者。但在香港醫療系統頻臨崩潰之際，網上流傳一段香港警察為醫護打氣的短片，但內容並非為香港醫護打氣，而是以普通話或廣東話向武漢醫護加油，全段片完全無提及香港醫護。短片中有21名警員發言，但僅3人露面，其他人均戴上口罩或蒙面，甚至有人僅旁白，完全沒有現身。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【武漢肺炎】港鐵證高鐵外判工發燒到醫院求醫 要求全綫員工戴口罩當值<br />\n<br />\n短片全長3分51秒，開首以簡體字寫出「<span style=\"color: red;\">親愛的武漢同胞</span>，我們是微博上的一群香港的警察，我們有話對您說」，接着便播出21名警員的打氣自拍片段，有人說「武漢同胞，我們支持你」、「武漢加油，我們香港警察支持你們」、「<span style=\"color: red;\">你們並不孤單，我們香港警察支持你們</span>，也謝謝大家一直以來支持我們，<span style=\"color: red;\">一方有難，我們</span>八方<span style=\"color: red;\">會支援</span>」、「祖國加油」等，有人身穿警服，更有多人似乎是身處警署內拍攝有關片段。但片段中大部份人均沒有露面，部份人以特效卡通遮蔽容貌，亦有人戴上口罩、蒙面或只拍攝眼睛以下面孔，更有人僅拍攝寫上「<span style=\"color: red;\">齊心抗疫</span> 醫護加油 支持你們！加油」或「<span style=\"color: red;\">警察勁揪</span>」的紙張，配上打氣旁白，完全沒有現身，未知<span style=\"color: red;\">不敢露面</span>的用意何在。<br />\n<br />\n片末則以簡體字寫上「向所有奮鬥在一綫的醫護人員致敬！武漢加油！中國加油！祝願全國人民身體健康」，但全片均無提及香港市民，或同時為香港醫護打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死黑警唔係歧視大陸哩覺得佢地有毒, 怕死唔敢返支那救人下,<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係死黑警冇料到所以唔敢露面得個講字, 刷下存在感做freerider呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"1a9f067efbafd9e79ef8acf8986db1d0da36b028","tid":1848828,"uid":294555,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:27:36.000Z","msg":"我支持香港警察，你地可以去武漢了"},{"pid":"d1b09f038d44dc7cc8d98fb1c666dd61fefcb1f9","tid":1848828,"uid":127929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:28:43.000Z","msg":"支持警察去武漢做救人英雄, 唔去正契弟正黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a34c074ab4656b9d0425b0638c7b6cc799e3bf","tid":1848828,"uid":256620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:29:09.000Z","msg":"[行動]129黎明行動 召喚嘔吐師-<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1848751/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1848751/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JjbXxpE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJjbXxpE.jpg&h=80c8210c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be0995bbfd2b8be50a5b722e0daf4ca7581abf98","tid":1848828,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:32:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">支持武汉同胞到警署找警察治疗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412ba5dfb59b1d89173cbe87f43e9c0961502be3","tid":1848828,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DtKWpn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DtKWpn.jpg&h=a27c226a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白色，是醫護常用顏色。不含任何色素，並容易發現污漬，適用於醫院最應保持潔淨的地方。除此之外，白色還代表純粹的善良和堅定的信念。<br />\n<br />\n當日，醫護們憑藉良心忠實履行自己的使命。今日，政權道德綁架他們這一份熱誠和信念。<br />\n<br />\n他們守護了我們生命和健康，但又誰能守護他們？<br />\n<br />\n全城白絲帶，支持醫護罷工。醫護不是condom，我們與醫護同行。<br />\n<br />\n#全城白絲帶 #撐醫護 #撐罷工 #封關口 #醫護非condom #與醫護同行<br />\n#香港金總 #HKFU #standwithmedics<br />\n<br />\n各位金融人都麻煩幫手填問卷，謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️⚠️緊急⚠️⚠️<br />\n<br />\n香港金融業職工共同抗疫意見調查<br />\n<br />\n香港金融業職工總會欲以問卷方式詢問同業以工業行動共同抗疫的意願和意見，以制定有效方式向僱主及政府表達對僱員對於安全和健康的憂慮，全民共同抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n由於事態緊急，如策劃任何工業行動必需經過既定程序。故此是次問卷將於1月31日23:59截止。希望同業們積極參與此調查，讓金總能全面理解金融界僱主於防疫措施現況，以及會員和同業於共同抗疫的意願，以制定下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/toVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FtoVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGXdC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=02746d0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/toVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7</a><br />\n<br />\n原post傳送門：<br />\n［行動］［請置頂］全民白絲帶 罷工撐醫護<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848612</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0d15d1a86d13d025095d0897c3455024c820543a","tid":1848828,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21247e2bf82a4a8598c876a167b2fd57ba75c676","tid":1848828,"uid":235824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:35:02.000Z","msg":"我們八方會支援  <br />\n<br />\n快D啦"},{"pid":"fc2ff535e5646fd4666e3fa278f9fec88c46b7ef","tid":1848828,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:38:32.000Z","msg":"去武漢親身支援未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de166c8a138981187741a249027eb3dd7fd3f68","tid":1848828,"uid":343712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:43:24.000Z","msg":"啱呀，依家武漢亂，上去幫手維持治安啦亞洲第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06bb4cb60d0d2cf54cf1bc8cdd460ea7cf7b40e","tid":1848828,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d736972f5ba19286b77bc71db58f5163cf93fcbe","tid":1848828,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc2ff535e5646fd4666e3fa278f9fec88c46b7ef","tid":1848828,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:38:32.000Z","msg":"去武漢親身支援未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P8gHJjH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP8gHJjH.jpg&h=a5237921&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45b0f30bc6c7df21ac9f689b8a190be208337062","tid":1848828,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d1b09f038d44dc7cc8d98fb1c666dd61fefcb1f9","tid":1848828,"uid":127929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:28:43.000Z","msg":"支持警察去武漢做救人英雄, 唔去正契弟正黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UXeFvxG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUXeFvxG.jpg&h=b8e76266&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d954c94864934fa068a81b6ae585487600a281e9","tid":1848828,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:53:39.000Z","msg":"快啲去武漢打氣啦"},{"pid":"61250b47595398bfa0e1838398f2e15e2ef719bf","tid":1848828,"uid":345689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:33:34.000Z","msg":"香港警察，仲唔快啲去武漢支援親愛嘅同胞？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"45b0f30bc6c7df21ac9f689b8a190be208337062","tid":1848828,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UXeFvxG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUXeFvxG.jpg&h=b8e76266&s={SIZE}\" />"}}